data.description:
2026 Maybury Ave, Flint, MI 48503 is a single family home that contains 884 sq ft and was built in 1957. It contains 3 bedrooms and 1 bathroom. This home last sold for $60,000 in August 2021. 
 
The Zestimate for this house is $68,300. The Rent Zestimate for this home is $1,033/mo.
